    42→/// <summary>
    43→///     AWS Lambda entry-point that ingests calendar/KPI telemetry from a Kinesis
    44→///     stream, dispatches each record to a KPI strategy, and writes the
    45→///     calculated result to Kinesis Data Firehose.
